detaileddescription.para:
Reconstruct the path to the goal position given a set of child/parent pairs. A child position was visited from the parent position when running the planning algorithm.
parents
a map of child/parent relationships. Keys are children, values are parents.
goal_pos
goal position, is assumed to have no children.
path
container where the path is be stored. The first element is the start position, the last element - goal position.
